## Appendix A — SimGrid layer inventory (dataIds)

All 136 grids parse with the 55-byte header `size, crc, mem, u16 major, u8, u32 ownType,
u32 dataId, u32 ?, u32 ?, u32 xSize, u32 zSize, u32 0, f32 16.0, f32 0.0625` followed by
raw cell data. Grid resolutions in this save: 128×128 (1 tile/cell), 64×64, 32×32, 16×16.
DataIds are the game's GUIDs for each data layer (power, pollution, land value, crime,
